definitions.definition: A lake in Cumbria , England , formerly divided between Lancashire and Westmorland .
A town near this lake in Windermere and Bowness parish, Westmorland and Furness district, Cumbria , previously in South Lakeland district ( OS grid ref SD4198 ) .
A town in Orange County , Florida , United States .
A rural locality in Bundaberg Region, Queensland , Australia .
A rural locality north-east of Hinds , Canterbury , New Zealand .
